    "description": "Outcome cohort: First CSS Total Score measurement >= 30, indicating severe functional impairment. The CSS Total Score (concept 2000001000) ranges 0-47, with higher scores indicating greater severity. A threshold of 30 places patients in the most severe quartile (dataset mean = 22.3). Index date is first measurement date reaching this threshold. Used as outcome in SCCS analysis examining AED polypharmacy effects.",
